AkFileID AkExternalSourceInfo::idFile

File ID. If not zero, the source will be streaming from disk. This ID can be anything. Note that you must override the low-level IO to resolve this ID to a real file. See streamingmanager_lowlevel for more information on overriding the Low Level IO.
